An '''ammo canister''' was a small container of small arms ammunition. Because of its miniature size, a canister was generally limited to one to two clips of ammo and a few grenades.<ref name="BF I guide">[[Star Wars Battlefront: Prima Official Game Guide|''Star Wars Battlefront'': Prima Official Game Guide]]</ref> During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] and the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], engineers and pilots commonly carried such canisters to readily resupply their allies with ammunition.

It was often designed with a glowing [[Color/Legends|red]] line around its cap that blinked on and off along with the words "AMMO SUPPLY" printed in [[Aurebesh/Legends|Aurebesh]] along its side.

